text: @FedEx  @FedExHelp :-( i am soooo very tired of trying to get answers from #Louisville management about misdelivered and missing packages. How do I contact someone who can/will follow through and actually help me resolve my issues - please respond with name and contact info
@gwendolynkelly Hello Gwendolyn, my name is Mary. I will be happy to check on your shipments for you. Please DM your name, delivery address, tracking and phone number. Thank you.
